      <div class="callout">
        <p><strong>No USCIS biometrics fee:</strong> Unlike many other applications, the I-130 for immediate relatives doesn't require a separate biometrics fee. The $675 covers the full petition filing. For a full line-item cost breakdown, see the <SmartLink href="/cr1-visa-cost">CR-1 visa cost guide</SmartLink>.</p>
